  "time_ut": 1661868349,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7  \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The development officer was attacked by her husband with a sharp weapon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Midrigiri police say that a development officer who was attached to the Midrigiri local secretariat was assaulted by her husband with a sharp weapon on the Viharamawata road in Midrigiri after a family dispute escalated.",
        "Police say that the development officer who was injured by the sharp weapon was seriously injured and admitted to Midrigiri Base Hospital and then transferred to Polonnaruwa General Hospital for further treatment.",
        "This officer is a mother of one child and there has been a dispute between the two for some time and this officer came to Medirigiriya police today on the 30th and made a complaint and while she was going home with another officer, the husband who is said to have come in a three-wheeler stopped the motorcycle that they were said to be traveling on. The police say that she was beaten with a weapon.",
        "The police have found the knife with which she was allegedly beaten and injured at the scene, and her husband has now fled the country. The police said that investigations have been started to arrest the suspect.",
        "Midrigiriya Police Station Commander Chief Police Inspector W.A.L Withanage and other officials are conducting further investigations."
      ],
